  "subject": "Collect PDP stats via a separate subscription",
  "commit_message": "Collect PDP stats via a separate subscription\n\nAdded a second subscription to the POLICY-PDP-PAP topic on which PDP\nstatistics are collected.  This topic uses a shared consumer group so\nthat only one PAP will receive a given message, thus preventing the same\nset of statistics from being written to the DB by multiple PAPs.\n\nAlso modified the first subscription so that it no longer updates the\nstatistics table.\n\nNote: collection of statistics is controlled by the topic configuration;\nif the topic, POLICY-STATISTICS, exists, then statistics are collected.\nOtherwise, they are not.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-3405\nChange-Id: I81471f82cff6efac5a59612d3f6af0513022806f\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
